00:01:32.020 --> 00:01:34.970
So there are three power weapons - a sniper
rifle, concussion rifle, and boltshot.

00:01:34.970 --> 00:01:38.020
The sniper has a ninety second respawn timer with zero spare clips,

00:01:38.020 --> 00:01:43.250
so that means four shots total. The concussion rifle has a 120 second respawn timer with zero spare clips,

00:01:43.250 --> 00:01:46.500
and the boltshot has a 120 second timer with one spare clip.

00:01:46.500 --> 00:01:49.579
Now the thing about these weapons that
makes them different than the others

00:01:49.579 --> 00:01:53.759
Besides the fact that they're power weapons of course, is that these three weapons are drop spawned

00:01:53.759 --> 00:01:57.540
Now let's see if I can explain drop spawning for those of you that don't know.

00:01:57.540 --> 00:02:01.479
So a weapon's respawn timer starts after that weapon has been moved

00:02:01.479 --> 00:02:02.320
from it's resting position

00:02:02.320 --> 00:02:06.570
which in most cases is whenever somebody picks it up, and because of this

00:02:06.570 --> 00:02:09.450
it's difficult to tell when a
certain weapon will spawn again if you

00:02:09.450 --> 00:02:11.550
don't know exactly when it's respawn timer started.

00:02:11.550 --> 00:02:15.099
However in the case of a drop spawned
weapon, that weapon spawns in the air

00:02:15.099 --> 00:02:15.890
and falls to the ground

00:02:15.890 --> 00:02:19.690
so that timer automatically starts as
soon as that weapons spawns

00:02:19.690 --> 00:02:24.060
and because of that, drop spawning,
drop spawned weapons appear on the map in

00:02:24.060 --> 00:02:24.790
certain intervals

00:02:24.790 --> 00:02:27.810
which eliminates any randomness that
could occur with

00:02:27.810 --> 00:02:31.560
with regular weapon spawns. So being able
to time your weapons is crucial if you really

00:02:31.560 --> 00:02:32.650
want to outplay your opponent,

00:02:32.650 --> 00:02:36.269
and using the game timer at the bottom
right of the screen definitely comes in handy.

00:02:36.269 --> 00:02:36.629
 

00:02:36.629 --> 00:02:40.610
