that the timers actually start

00:02:40.610 --> 00:02:41.970
10 seconds before the match begins

00:02:41.970 --> 00:02:45.760
so let's look at the sniper for example. Even though the game started at 15 minutes

00:02:45.760 --> 00:02:49.959
the weapon timer started at 15 minutes
and 10 seconds so that means with a 90

00:02:49.959 --> 00:02:50.790
second respawn timer

00:02:50.790 --> 00:02:53.970
the weapon will respawn at 13
minutes and 40 seconds not 30

00:02:53.970 --> 00:02:54.410
seconds.

00:02:54.410 --> 00:02:58.290
So like I said being able to keep
track of your respawn times for all your

00:02:58.290 --> 00:03:00.780
